          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/214/5858774/VO_110_Stormward_Baelgrim_89_M.ogg",
          "text": "Koratite, what are you doing? Stop this!",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251819,
          "filename": "vo-110-stormward-baelgrim-111-m",
          "fileDataId": 5858844,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/28/5858844/VO_110_Stormward_Baelgrim_111_M.ogg",
          "text": "Agreed. Vokmar, engage the target!",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 248949,
          "filename": "vo-110-stormward-baelgrim-45-m",
          "fileDataId": 5782545,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/17/5782545/VO_110_Stormward_Baelgrim_45_M.ogg",
          "text": "And without the Stormriders...",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251796,
          "filename": "vo-110-stormward-baelgrim-88-m",
          "fileDataId": 5858773,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/213/5858773/VO_110_Stormward_Baelgrim_88_M.ogg",
          "text": "Go! Find Vokmar! He will take you to safety!",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251818,
          "filename": "vo-110-stormward-baelgrim-110-m",
          "fileDataId": 5858843,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/27/5858843/VO_110_Stormward_Baelgrim_110_M.ogg",
          "text": "I have seen nothing like it. Its energies have twisted them, changing them into... this!",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251790,
          "filename": "vo-110-stormward-baelgrim-82-m",
          "fileDataId": 5858767,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/207/5858767/VO_110_Stormward_Baelgrim_82_M.ogg",
          "text": "I left Gorren, my second, in charge of the Stormperch when I left to investigate your Dalaran's crash.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251793,
          "filename": "vo-110-stormward-baelgrim-85-m",
          "fileDataId": 5858770,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/210/5858770/VO_110_Stormward_Baelgrim_85_M.ogg",
          "text": "I will deactivate Gorren myself for this sacrilege.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251804,
          "filename": "vo-110-stormward-baelgrim-96-m",
          "fileDataId": 5858809,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/249/5858809/VO_110_Stormward_Baelgrim_96_M.ogg",
          "text": "It is done. The corruption was been eliminated, but we were too late.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251806,
          "filename": "vo-110-stormward-baelgrim-98-m",
          "fileDataId": 5858811,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/251/5858811/VO_110_Stormward_Baelgrim_98_M.ogg",
          "text": "Let us return to the Council. I... must report to them.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251800,
          "filename": "vo-110-stormward-baelgrim-92-m",
          "fileDataId": 5858777,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/217/5858777/VO_110_Stormward_Baelgrim_92_M.ogg",
          "text": "May your memory be forever cursed by what you have wrought here!",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251805,
          "filename": "vo-110-stormward-baelgrim-97-m",
          "fileDataId": 5858810,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/250/5858810/VO_110_Stormward_Baelgrim_97_M.ogg",
          "text": "Nearly our entire order has been wiped out. The Stormriders can protect Dornogal no longer.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251792,
          "filename": "vo-110-stormward-baelgrim-84-m",
          "fileDataId": 5858769,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/209/5858769/VO_110_Stormward_Baelgrim_84_M.ogg",
          "text": "Rest well, Kyrioss. You deserved a better rider than Gorren.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251802,
          "filename": "vo-110-stormward-baelgrim-94-m",
          "fileDataId": 5858807,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/247/5858807/VO_110_Stormward_Baelgrim_94_M.ogg",
          "text": "Take out the creatures channeling on that core!",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251801,
          "filename": "vo-110-stormward-baelgrim-93-m",
          "fileDataId": 5858778,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/218/5858778/VO_110_Stormward_Baelgrim_93_M.ogg",
          "text": "The same dark magic that was emanating from the Stormriders is more powerful here.",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251795,
          "filename": "vo-110-stormward-baelgrim-87-m",
          "fileDataId": 5858772,
          "audioUrl": "https://wow.zamimg.com/sound-ids/live/enus/212/5858772/VO_110_Stormward_Baelgrim_87_M.ogg",
          "text": "Their edict has been change by some... dark influence!",
          "status": "pending",
          "selected": false,
          "notes": ""
        },
        {
          "soundId": 251787,
          "filename": "vo-110-stormward-baelgrim-79-m",
